name: PixWave
description: PixWave is a PHP microservice wallet system that processes payments via PIX using two gateways, ensuring high availability and fallback. It uses MySQL for records, Redis for caching, SNS for messaging, Docker and Kubernetes for orchestration, and centralizes logs with Logstash and Elasticsearch.

name: Nexus-Dynamic-Docker-Routing
description: Nexus is a reverse proxy and container management system for Docker environments. It routes traffic to containers based on subdomains and provides a simple API for management. Features include real-time Docker event listening, automatic service discovery, and WebSocket support, simplifying microservices deployment in Docker ecosystems.
